quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  10,43,"Ne mubo baliwo bakhukhondiolanga. Koo, onyala okhulunjisia abawofu kata nibalanyala okhulola tawe?"
  10,44,"Toto Nyasaye shakholelangakhwo abandu obubii tawe, halali abandu abeene nibo bekholelanga obubii."
  10,45,"Ne inyanga ya alibakhung’asia, iliba shinga shibekhala khushialo halali Isaa ndala sa yeshitere. Balimanyana. Toto basikha balia bakatsula okhubukana nende Nyasaye, ne shibaali bokhulunjikha tawe."
  10,46,"Ne toto nikhukhwechesia malala khuka khubalakanga, nohomba nikhukhufwisia, khwifwe niko amakalushilo kenyu, mana Nyasaye aliba omuloli khukabakholanga."
  10,47,"Ne buli omukanda kuli nende Omurumwa. Kho olwa Omurumwa wabu alibetsera, balibusilibwa eshina hakari wabu mubuleng’aafu, ne bo shibalikholelwa obubii tawe."
  10,48,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Niliina akamulakanga kano, toto nimuli abahabwene?”"
  10,49,"Boola mbu; “Esie embula obunyali bwokhwikholela obubii nohomba obulayi tawe, halali shia Nyasaye yenya. Buli omukanda kuli nende ebise biakwo. Ebise biabu nibiula, shibanyala okhwikhala isaa ndala nohomba shibanyala okhuranjilila tawe.""
  10,50,"Boola mbu; “Mulola murie eshinyasio esho nishibetsela eshilo nohomba eshitere, kho shina shiayo shia abamabii bashiyungubalilanga mbu shitse lwangu?’’"
  10,51,"Mana olwa ilirulila khomwaisuubila? Mulirebwa mbu; “Bulaano buri (isayino), ne mwali nimuiyungubalilanga?""
  10,52,"Mana balia bakhola obubii baliboolelwa mbu; “Pile eshinyasio shilawa tawe. Koo, mukharungwakho eshindi eshilali eshamwakholanga?”"
  10,53,"Ne bakhurebanga mbu; "Koo, ako ni katoto?” Boola mbu; “Eeeh, nditsuba khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi mbu toto ako ni habwene. Ne enywe shimunyala okhushila tawe.”"